{"tid":438413,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"邱騰華: 市區舊樓寬頻入屋是商業考慮，政府不計劃介入","createTime":"2017-10-17T01:52:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-17T06:18:28.000Z","uid":12599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"af822c46df2243d906ad6a6ac3f0771c235a4326","tid":438413,"uid":12599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T01:52:50.000Z","msg":"立法會一個委員會，討論施政報告中的資訊科技及創意產業政策。香港本土毛孟靜指政府計劃資助為偏遠地區鋪設寬頻，但同時<span style=\"color: red;\">市區舊樓上網費用高昂欠缺選擇，希望政府關注</span>；旅遊界姚思榮指，政府免費wifi 熱點部分上網功能欠佳，要求改善。<br />\n<br />\n商務及經濟發展局長邱騰華表示，政府計劃擴展光纖網絡至三百多條偏遠村落，預計需時五年，但<span style=\"color: red;\">市區舊樓寬頻入屋是商業考慮，政府不計劃介入</span>。創新及科技局長楊偉雄指，wifi科技日新月異，政府正檢討提升相關科技。"},{"pid":"0d21a63cda4fb00d70abcc5859b8d79ff542f40b","tid":438413,"uid":45353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T05:04:50.000Z","msg":"其實d舊樓附近有幾幢新樓<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n就自然會拉埋光x去舊樓區<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1c0507a049359c9c22e370fe5a5711194761cce","tid":438413,"uid":45213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T05:07:21.000Z","msg":"屌你老母商業考慮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afa17dea65d54015304b1f08268d984b920787be","tid":438413,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T05:07:42.000Z","msg":"Oct 17近期活躍五毛<br />\n1三色貓<br />\n2群龍共舞<br />\n3法國佬巫斯義=香港鍵國<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">4真律師何君堯</span><br />\n5newlife<br />\n6侵B<br />\n7返六日唔撚易<br />\n8dewi<br />\n9bb chu<br />\n10優美開始"},{"pid":"60842bc562c638906af42403a51ad58f33de4e4d","tid":438413,"uid":78968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T05:09:38.000Z","msg":"我住緊果棟都無光纖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a269313dcdfc7d5d4fbe848c67f07dd94c266add","tid":438413,"uid":8071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T05:20:49.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><blockquote>創新及科技局長